edge: The lead single from the film's soundtrack, 'For You', performed by Rita Ora and Liam Payne, was released on January 5, 2018. The soundtrack's track list was released on January 8, 2018, including artists Julia Michaels, Sia, Jessie J, Black Atlass, Ellie Goulding, Hailee Steinfeld, Dua Lipa, Rita Ora, Liam Payne and Miike Snow on the 22-song album. The soundtrack debuted at #5 on Billboard 200 chart with 58,000 equivalent album units.
